dct_title_s: Geology resources and constraints Monterey County, California
dct_description_sm: "This CD-ROM contains a comprehensive database of the geology resources and constraints of Monterey County, California."

Includes ESRI shapefiles for geologic units, faults, earthquakes, landslide and liquefaction susceptibility, erosion potential, minerals, mines, oil wells, aquifer recharge, and paleontological resources.
This information was prepared for the Monterey County General Plan Update.
System requirements: CD-ROM drive; monitor supporting 256 or more colors; word processing program; Adobe Acrobat reader; Internet web browser; ESRI ArcExplorer.
